### 11. CURRENT USAGE IN MyOrdersRewardProgram

**Current Approach (React Components):**
- `/src/screens/MyOrdersRewardProgram/index.tsx`: Logic hook with Zustand store access
- `/src/screens/MyOrdersRewardProgram/view.tsx`: Presentation with FlatList and CardVehicleTags
